# Architecture Review (Phase 23)

Read **[ARCHITECTURE_REVIEW.md](../../ARCHITECTURE_REVIEW.md)** before large refactors or new surface areas.

## Stabilization rules

1. **No new major features** until Customer App migration milestones are met (Phase 24)
2. Canonical customer routes are **`/app/*`** — `/dashboard/*` is legacy; do not add new dashboard-only pages
3. **Platform Admin** must not become the customer daily workspace
4. Declare **Feature owner** before every implementation (see [layer-ownership.mdc](./layer-ownership.mdc))
5. `/platform/metrics` ≠ `/platform/impact` — business KPIs vs anonymised proof
6. `/platform/executive` ≠ customer Executive Dashboard — different layers when building `/app/executive`
7. Install runtime: `/api/install/*` + `/api/embed/*` (+ `/api/installations/*` for wizard)
8. Do not store customer email/chat/order content in platform metrics or audit tables

## Next priority

Customer App migration: move `app/dashboard/*` → `app/app/*`, unify nav on `lib/app/nav-config.ts`.
